e conclude that the transitions for\nXY and Heisenberg frustrated magnets are of first order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2010 20:36:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2011 11:14:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-12-30"}
